OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fcloudy evening and night with some
OL,7,Fhaar at times. Rain spreads north in
OL,8,Fthe evening, drier overnight but still
OL,9,Fwith some showery rain. Becoming
OL,10,Fbreezier later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FDull start with some haar,
OL,13,Fbut brightening up, then rather cloudy
OL,14,Fbut with a few sunny intervals along
OL,15,Fwith the odd shower. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
