OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSunny
OL,6,Fintervals and a few showers on Friday.
OL,7,FDry and bright start Saturday with
OL,8,Fsome sunshine before rain and wind in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Sunny spells and
OL,10,Foccasional rain on Sunday
